. -----------------
.
. Field     Type            Length    From - To      Description
.---------------------------------------------------------------------------
APPaid        RECORD
AccountNumber DIM               6
TransYear     DIM               2
TransMonth    DIM               2
TransDay      DIM               2
Invoice       DIM               6
Counter       FORM              1
Description   DIM               20
Amount        FORM              6.2
LastDiscDay   DIM               8
DiscountAmt   FORM              4.2
CheckNumber   DIM               6
PaidDate      DIM               8
GLCode        DIM               6
              RECORDEND
